                     <interp inst="t18320906-294-person2434" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am in the employ of Mr. John Graham and others - they are <rs id="t18320906-294-viclabel1663" type="occupation">upholsterer</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-294-victim2432 t18320906-294-viclabel1663"></join>s. This is their property; I saw it safe in the afternoon of the 26th of July - I know nothing of the prisoners.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320906-294-person2435">
                  JOSEPH 
                  HIGGINS
               <interp inst="t18320906-294-person2435" type="surname" value="HIGGINS"></interp>
